    Implement fixtures, score events, and scoring engine
    
    - Fix Prisma Studio connection: Use standard Postgres URL (port 5432)
    - Update Prisma schema: Add EventType enum, fixture score fields, ScoreEvent minute field
    - Add migration: Convert ScoreEvent.type to enum, add fixture scoring fields
    - Create fixtures helper utilities: getFixturesWithRelations, getPlayersForFixture, etc.
    - Implement scoring engine: calculatePlayerPoints() with confirmed rules
      - GOAL: +5, ASSIST: +3, OWN_GOAL: -2
      - YELLOW_CARD: -1, RED_CARD: -3
      - GK: 7 - goalsConceded (can be negative)
      - Outfield clean sheet: +1 if goalsConceded == 0
    - Add server actions: fixtures CRUD, score events CRUD, runGameweekScoring
    - Build admin UI: fixtures list, fixture detail, events management pages
    - Update gameweek scoring action to use new calculatePlayerPoints function
    - Add documentation: DATABASE_URL_SETUP.md, connection troubleshooting guides

